data.description: Bring all offers. Unpack and move right in. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the thoughtfully designed layout that maximizes both space and functionality. The main floor boasts an open concept kitchen, dining, and living area, creating a seamless flow that is perfect for entertaining friends and family. The kitchen is equipped with brand-new stainless-steel appliances, adding a touch of modern elegance to the space. Upstairs, you'll find three spacious bedrooms, providing ample room for relaxation and privacy. The master bedroom features an ensuite bathroom, ensuring convenience and comfort. Additionally, the laundry area is conveniently located on the upper level, making chores a breeze. The flooring has been updated with new LVP 20mm protective flooring, AC 2020. Schedule your showing today
